# WTXUP Broadcom BCM943602CS Wi-Fi 1300Mbps Dual Band 802.11ac Bluetooth 4.1

This is a natively supported chipset
- Wi-Fi: BCM943602 - VEN_0x14E3 DEV_0x43BA, natively supported till macOS 13 Ventura
- Bluetooth
  - At first install, it's a BCM2045A0 - USB VEN_0x0A5C DEV_0x21FF
  - After Windows Bootcamp driver installation it becomes an BCM20703 - USB VEN_0x05AC DEV_0x8290, which is native supported

## Install
- Boot Windows
- Use Brigadier to download BootCamp for iMac19,1
- Install $WinPEDriver$\BroadcomWirelessNIC\bcmwl63.inf
- Install $WinPEDriver$\AppleBluetoothBroadcom\AppleBTBC.inf

## Wi-Fi for >= macOS 14 Sonoma
- Use Apple Broadcom Wi-Fi Companion
